{"tid":569858,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[ Netflix]Jared Leto 、淺野忠信主演新戲—局外人","createTime":"2018-02-23T06:01:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T03:48:45.000Z","uid":10626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8d6e3c5e00b49c11238a622cb0436b68a3ea1fb0","tid":569858,"uid":10626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:01:20.000Z","msg":"丹麥導演馬丁贊維李特（Martin Zandvliet）在 2015 年帶來《拆彈少年》（Land of Mine）並廣獲好評之後，最新執導作品將帶給觀眾的則是在好萊塢打滾許久的《局外人》（The Outsider），終於在今天釋出了首支預告。<br />\n<br />\n此片最早在 2012 年由華納兄弟影業籌拍，最初的導演與主演人選是《狡兔計劃》丹尼爾伊斯皮諾薩（Daniel Espinosa）與麥可法斯賓達（Michael Fassbender）；隔年又宣布此片將作為日本導演三池崇史的第一部英語電影，並有望找來湯姆哈迪（Tom Hardy）主演，但隨後兩人皆因檔期衝突而退出；最後在 2016 年選定馬丁贊維李特執導，金獎男配角傑瑞德里托（Jared Leto）主演，同年底在東京開拍，並由 Netflix 取得全球發行權。<br />\n<br />\n演出卡司還包括淺野忠信、椎名桔平、忽那汐里、大森南朋、田中泯，官方劇情描述：一名在戰後日本被囚禁的美國士兵，進入極道的陰暗世界，融入他們的生態以償還自由。將在 3 月 9 日全球同步上線。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3kUlga6ZxGM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3kUlga6ZxGM&d=czLhboHiFNV%2BMEKCeGGQ0zM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=3b0dc5eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3kUlga6ZxGM</a>"},{"pid":"7345f5248555009d8847cf6803fa5a0092c44dce","tid":569858,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T16:14:10.000Z","msg":"Netflix魔咒！！！"},{"pid":"86d8f340b655478f98c238d26464e409323bec7f","tid":569858,"uid":8809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T16:45:48.000Z","msg":"Jared Leto<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80213dc1f0eace956b2b17dff12aa9fa1fa96b83","tid":569858,"uid":61317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T19:35:05.000Z","msg":"淺野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc8ce2a921115733f0c49363104e02def22b04cd","tid":569858,"uid":48473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re